      "text": "我自愿作怪咖 就不怕被你笑话",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 187.25,
      "time_str": "03:07.250",
      "text": "你还有几次分开的话",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 191.77,
      "time_str": "03:11.770",
      "text": "新鲜感不佳词语匮乏",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 195.98,
      "time_str": "03:15.980",
      "text": "感情里的怪咖 可手里也没筹码",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 203.5,
      "time_str": "03:23.500",
      "text": "所以要找个缓冲方法",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 207.43,
      "time_str": "03:27.430",
      "text": "直到有天我也放得下",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 211.67,
      "time_str": "03:31.670",
      "text": "我不是个怪咖 是不计较的惩罚",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 221.42,
      "time_str": "03:41.420",
      "text": "感情里的怪咖 再难过也笑着说吧",
      "translation": null
